      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>BERGSTEIN--Leonard. Loving husband, father, and grandfather. Survived by his wife Marilyn, three daughters, seven grandchildren, and all of those who had the good fortune of knowing him. He will be missed. Memorial Service at Riverside Nassau North Chapels, Great Neck, 2pm, April 23, 2007.</p>
